  "texts": [
    "Additionally, users can enter their own tasks in the chat box.",
    "After submitting a task, the agent will provide a visualization of the production and insights obtained from the calculations in the Visualization view (Fig. 4B).",
    "If the task needs to be decomposed, the task decomposition plan will appear.",
    "The user can modify the logical relationship between the task and the execution plan by switching the text button.",
    "The agent will analyze the task based on the user's instructions and return the results of multiple subtasks."
